OL,3,CLouvre Museum's director resigns
OL,4,Cfollowing jewels heist in Paris
OL,6,FThe director of the Louvre Museum has
OL,7,Fresigned, months after the high-
OL,8,Fprofile theft of France's crown jewels.
OL,10,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron on
OL,11,FTuesday accepted the resignation of
OL,12,FLaurence des Cars, who has been under
OL,13,Ffire in the wake of the heist at the
OL,14,Fworld's most visited museum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
