OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1771967126
OL,3,CLouvre Museum's director resigns
OL,4,Cfollowing jewels heist in Paris
OL,6,FIn a statement, the presidential
OL,7,Foffice said Macron praised des Cars'
OL,8,Fresignation decision as "an act of
OL,9,Fresponsibility at a time when the
OL,10,Fworld's largest museum needs calm and
OL,11,Fa strong new impetus to carry out
OL,12,Fmajor projects involving security
OL,13,Fupgrades, modernisation" and other
OL,14,Finitiatives.
OL,16,FThieves took less than eight minutes
OL,17,Fin October to steal #76 million worth
OL,18,Fof crown jewels in a weekend heist at
OL,19,Fthe iconic Louvre Museum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
