OL,3,CLouvre Museum's director resigns
OL,4,Cfollowing jewels heist in Paris
OL,6,FThey used an extendable ladder mounted
OL,7,Fon a truck to break through an
OL,8,Funmonitored window.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FTwo entered the building while two
OL,16,Fstayed on the ground. All four then
OL,17,Fescaped on motorbikes, but in their
OL,18,Fhaste, they dropped a diamond and
OL,19,Femerald crown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
