OL,3,CLouvre Museum's director resigns
OL,4,Cfollowing jewels heist in Paris
OL,6,FNumerous people have been detained
OL,7,Fsince the start of the investigation,
OL,8,Fwith authorities now believing they
OL,9,Fhave all four members of the team who
OL,10,Fwere directly involved in the heist in
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,FIn total, five people have been
OL,14,Fcharged in connection with the
OL,15,Fincident, including the four main crew
OL,16,Fmembers and the partner of one of them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
