OL,3,CLouvre Museum's director resigns
OL,4,Cfollowing jewels heist in Paris
OL,6,FHowever, the location of the jewels,
OL,7,Fincluding an emerald and diamond
OL,8,Fnecklace that Napoleon I had gifted
OL,9,Fhis second wife, Empress Marie-Louise,
OL,10,Fremains unknown.
OL,12,FSince the theft, security at the
OL,13,FLouvre has been transformed after its
OL,14,Foperators admitted it had been lacking.
OL,16,FSeveral of its most valuable items
OL,17,Fhave also been transferred to the Bank
OL,18,Fof France.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
