OL,6,FThe Louvre has also hiked prices for
OL,7,Fvisitors from non-EU countries in
OL,8,Frecent months, with it rising from 22
OL,9,Feuros (#19.25) to 32 euros (#28).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
